@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sgcttt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp((0.21 - v0))
    tmp = wp.exp(v2)
    v1 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.78 - tmp + 0.84)) + wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.13)))
    tmp = (v2 / ((v1 + 0.34 + v0 + 0.38) * 0.25))
    tmp = (0.04 - wp.cos(0.37))
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.36) + wp.cos(v2))
    tmp = ((tmp / (tmp + 0.08 + v2 + 0.16)) / ((v2 + 0.10 * v2 + 0.67) / (tmp + 0.21 - v1 + 0.29)))
    data[tid] = v0
